data.description: Welcome to your new Hollywood townhome! This beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is move-in ready and waiting for you. Step inside to find an open and spacious living area with gleaming tile flooring, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing after a long day.  The kitchen has been completely renovated with modern fixtures and high-end appliances, making cooking a joy. Upstairs, you'll find a luxurious master bedroom suite, complete with a newly updated bathroom, providing the perfect oasis for relaxation.  There are two additional bedrooms providing ample space for family or guests. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your own private outdoor space, perfect for barbecues and outdoor entertaining.
